summary: Reworked only the blurry vanilla textures. HD Version of the Farmhouse texture set.
descriptionHtml:
Reworked only the blurry vanilla textures. HD Version of the Farmhouse texture set.
All textures are based on vanilla textures with more detail applied to them to 
maintain the original look.

The complete farmhouse and village texture set is merged now with some aditional textures.
You can find it here: http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=4306
author: Ecmgecko
